::Const.Strings.PerkDescription.CloseCombatArcher = "If you can see the white in your enemy\'s eyes, aim for it! Damage is increased by [color=" + this.Const.UI.Color.PositiveValue + "]1%[/color] of your current Ranged Defense when using a ranged weapon (including throwing weapons) against a target 2 or less tiles away.\n\nDamage is increased by [color=" + this.Const.UI.Color.PositiveValue + "]1%[/color] for every 3 points of your current Ranged Defense against a target 3 tiles away. Reduces the maximum range of throwing weapons to [color=" + this.Const.UI.Color.NegativeValue + "]3[/color] tiles away.\n\nFor weapons above this range Damage will reduce by [color=" + this.Const.UI.Color.NegativeValue + "]5%[/color] of the Ranged Defense per distance traveled above 4. Hit chance will be also reduced by [color=" + this.Const.UI.Color.NegativeValue + "]3[/color] per distance traveled.";
::Const.Perks.PerkDefObjects[::Const.Perks.PerkDefs.CloseCombatArcher].Tooltip = ::Const.Strings.PerkDescription.CloseCombatArcher;
